Source: parolottero-languages
Section: games
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Salvo 'LtWorf' Tomaselli <tiposchi@tiscali.it>
Build-Depends:
 debhelper-compat (= 13),
 python3,
 wget,
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/ltworf/parolottero-languages
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/ltworf/parolottero-languages
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: parolottero-data-it
Provides: parolottero-data
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, parolottero
Architecture: all
Description: Compose words using a 4x4 grid of letters, Italian game files
 A word game intended for touch screens.
 .
 Players must drag their finger (or mouse) over random letters in a 4x4 grid
 to compose as many words as they can, until the time runs out.
 .
 This package contains the data files to play with Italian words.

